{"id":232965237,"title":"#一拳超人 #組隊建議","content":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/2b97eec0-17d5-4cca-ba4c-6228e80caba3/1280.jpeg\n以前SSR角色疫苗人、地底王很早抽到\n所以主要都打灼燒流輸出\n然後以黃金珠、獸王、傑諾斯輔助\n然後固定一個位置保留給無照騎士\n\n最近一直抽到坦角，順序大概是\n深海王>背心>獨角仙>超合金黑光\n\n現在覺得有八隻SSR有點難抉擇，\n突然不知道怎麼組隊，和養的順序\n目前想法是這樣：\n1 童帝核心（爆擊獲得能量）、地底王、疫苗人\n背心（同排盾）、獨角仙、獸王（受傷）\n\n2 深海王核心（反擊流）、阿修羅、超合金、背心\n+崩壞流（童帝、黃金珠）\n+受傷流（獸王、臭老臉）\n+灼燒流（地底王、疫苗人）\n\n因為傑諾斯好像很少用到了，所以就還原了\n目前不知道\nSSR的索尼克\nSR的甜心假面、青焰、無限昆布、彈簧鬍\n居合鐵、吉納斯博士這些角色的價值\n好像有點顧不到了\n\n我也是無課玩家，想跟各位討論，並尋求各位練角順序、組隊構成的建議","excerpt":"以前SSR角色疫苗人、地底王很早抽到，所以主要都打灼燒流輸出，然後以黃金珠、獸王、傑諾斯輔助，然後固定一個位置保留給無照騎士，最近一直抽到坦角，順序大概是，深海王>背心>獨角仙>超合金黑光，現在覺得有","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"72f262c4-75aa-4d75-ab0e-cd7bd09e69b5","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-27T05:14:31.908Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-27T05:14:31.908Z","commentCount":9,"likeCount":0,"tags":[],"topics":["一拳超人","組隊","建議"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"遊戲","forumAlias":"game","school":"銘傳大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":true,"reactions":[],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/2b97eec0-17d5-4cca-ba4c-6228e80caba3/1280.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"37da4af8-b513-43ae-ab17-6016b6ab5c04","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/2b97eec0-17d5-4cca-ba4c-6228e80caba3/640.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/2b97eec0-17d5-4cca-ba4c-6228e80caba3/640.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/2b97eec0-17d5-4cca-ba4c-6228e80caba3/640.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":[],"createdAt":"2020-01-27T05:14:31.908Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-27T05:14:31.908Z","width":640,"height":360},{"id":"37da4af8-b513-43ae-ab17-6016b6ab5c04","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/2b97eec0-17d5-4cca-b